Gadgets
- square bumper
- circular bumper
- triangular bumper
- flipper
- absorber
- outer wall (one of four)

Gadgets Methods
- handleBall -> return an event or null
- action
- getSize
- toString

Board
- width and height
- list of gadgets
- event queue
- step

Wall
- knows whether it is transport
- knows which wall it is on

BoardParser
- effectively a constructor for boards
- static method which reads a file and return a constructed board

PingballClient class
- has main method
- parses arguments

ServerConnection
- wraps the socket layer of communication
- gives us a java api to communicating.


---

Server

Thin server class
- just routes messages about ball transfer between client and server
